{"id":580758,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【立此存照】假外媒-真外宣：红衣女记者东家疑资/","date":"2018-03-14T03:59:39Z","modified":"2018-03-15T05:53:20Z","title":"【立此存照】假外媒 真外宣：红衣女记者东家疑资金来源造假","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日走红的“红衣女记者”张慧君就职的全美电视台，American Multimedia Television USA (AMTV)，前身是2004年由一位叫 Yong Qin 的人成立的一家名为 First Pacific Financial Investment Group Inc 的公司，2009年12月才更名为“AMTV”，现总裁名为Jason Quin。经工商文件签名对比，可以确认 Yong Qin 与 Jason Quin 是同一人（下附文件截图）。Jason Quin 目前的公开中文名为“秦嘉豪”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/红与蓝.gif\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-580763\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/红与蓝.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"261\" height=\"147\" /></a></p>\n<p>全美电视台官网用蹩脚英语写成的<a href=\"https://amtvusa.tv/about-amtv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">英文介绍</a>中，称该公司的<strong>“主要资金提供者”为两家分别名为 Franklin International Group 和 American Berkshire International Group 的公司</strong>。然而经中国数字时代编辑查询工商登记信息后发现，<strong>上述两家公司都由全美电视台老板 Jason Quin 控制，</strong>且其中一家已被加州政府吊销营业执照。很显然，<strong>全美电视台真实的资金来源并非如其公布的那般简单。</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_580769\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Book1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580769\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Book1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Book1.jpg 1036w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Book1-300x104.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Book1-768x265.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Book1-1024x354.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">点击图片查看大图</span></p></div>\n<p>另外，Jason Quin 同时也是在洛杉矶注册的非营利组织“美国国际商会 AICC”（American International Chamber of Commerce）的CEO。AICC <a href=\"https://aiccus.org/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%95%86%E4%BC%9A/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">官网</a>称该组织“<span class=\"st\">以致力于推动国际经济贸易发展、提高社会、经济及环境效益为宗旨”，是美国”最具权威的国际性商会之一“。</span></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E6%8F%90%E9%97%AE%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8C%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%99%BD%E7%9C%BC%E9%84%99%E8%A7%86/\">【弄个大新闻】两会红与蓝：白眼翻出假外媒</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/%E3%80%90%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D%E5%BA%93%E3%80%91%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E7%BF%BB%E7%99%BD%E7%9C%BC%E9%81%AD%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD-%E8%93%9D%E8%A1%A3%E8%AE%B0%E8%80%85%E6%88%90%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D/\">【敏感词库】两会翻白眼遭屏蔽 蓝衣记者成敏感词</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/bbc%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e4%b8%a4%e4%bc%9a%ef%bc%9a%e5%a5%b3%e8%ae%b0%e8%80%85%e7%bf%bb%e7%99%bd%e7%9c%bc%e8%a2%ab%e7%9b%b4%e6%92%ad%e5%bc%95%e7%88%86%e7%a4%be%e4%ba%a4%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BBC｜中国两会：女记者翻白眼被直播引爆社交网络</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_580759\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580759\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"474\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV2.jpg 1094w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV2-285x300.jpg 285w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV2-768x809.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV2-972x1024.jpg 972w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">2009年12月，全美电视台前身 First Pacific Financial Investment Group Inc 正式更名为“American Multimedia Television USA”(AMTV)；工商文件截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580760\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580760\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV1.jpg 962w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV1-260x300.jpg 260w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV1-768x886.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV1-887x1024.jpg 887w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">全美电视台前身 First Pacific Financial Investment Group Inc 于2004年3月在大洛杉矶地区Pasadena市登记成立；工商文件截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580761\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580761\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV3.jpg 1032w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV3-300x190.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV3-768x485.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV3-1024x647.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">全美电视台在美国联邦通信委员会（FCC）的注册信息，通信地址是位于加州Pasadena市的一处邮政信箱托管服务处，非实际地址；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580764\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/张慧君-赵忠祥.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580764\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/张慧君-赵忠祥.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"353\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/张慧君-赵忠祥.jpg 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/张慧君-赵忠祥-300x202.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">2015年，“红衣女记者”张慧君与赵忠祥一起主持宣传“红色文化”的活动；网络图片</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580772\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Yong-Qin2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580772\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Yong-Qin2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"518\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Yong-Qin2.jpg 1190w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Yong-Qin2-290x300.jpg 290w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Yong-Qin2-768x795.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/Yong-Qin2-989x1024.jpg 989w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">秦先生去年与特朗普的合照；网络报道截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_580767\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-580767\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"920\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV4.jpg 1611w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV4-163x300.jpg 163w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV4-768x1413.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/AMTV4-556x1024.jpg 556w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">全美电视台官网的英语介绍错误百出，让人无法直视；网页截图</span></p></div>\n<p>两会翻白眼，翻出一个以海外华媒之名，行中共外宣之实，资金来源成疑的“全美电视台”。</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[34076,24832,20377,9006,34121,34125,34122]}